Yeeee a Gay WebServer, for now it supports only static pages :)

Compiled with:
   
    g++-4.5.3
    nspr-4.8.9

To compile:

    g++ `nspr-config --cflags --libs` -o xzHTTPd src/*.cpp src/*.hpp

Description:

    Server     - This is the main class, it provides to receive requests and create/join threads
    Socket     - Just a beautiful socket management class :333
    Config     - Parse and keep configuration parameters read from config file
    Exception  - Let's handle exceptions in a good way
    Client     - Each client connected
    Log        - This checks always what you do, stay alert
    Utility    - Useful stuff 
